=====CLI Terminal Module=====
$nomention
```
CLI Terminal
User: $username
----------------
$help - Commands
$support - DMs you a link to the support server
$exp - Get experimental bot
$build
More Comming Soon!
```
=====XBP Bot=====
$nomention
```
XBP
User: $username
==============
>help - Lists commands
>build - Shows bot info
>support - DMs you a support link
>CLI - Get CLI bot for discord
>more - More Commands
```
